description: Corem Property Group AB engages in acquiring and managing real properties. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 61 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2000-06-26. The Company’s property portfolio comprises properties primarily located in the south of Sweden, in regions such as Rosersberg and Arninge in Stockholm, Oresund, Vast, Smaland and Malardalen/Norr, as well as in Copenhagen, Denmark. The firm operates Corem AB as a wholy owned subsidiary.
name: Corem Property Group AB
